Title: Dude Ranch
Plot: While vacationing on Lost Creek Ranch, the three families try their hands at a little cattle herding, skeet shooting and horseback riding. There are also some big firsts, a huge surprise and an actual face-off between Jay and a cowboy named Hank.
ParentalRatingReason: PG Coarse language and sexual references
Writer: Paul Corrigan, Brad Walsh, Dan O'Shannon
GuestStars: Reid Ewing, Tim Blake Nelson, Matthew Gumley
